data.description: Move right into this charming and delightful, well-maintained home with approx 1700 square feet of living space all on one floor with a finished lower level Rec Room. The remodeled and generous sized kitchen has plenty of cabinets with expansive counter space for all your culinary needs. Each of the three bedrooms, with ample closet space have 2023 new carpets with hardwood floors underneath. The lower-level recreation room has 2023 new carpet too. The glass slider from the dining room leads to the patio and large, fully fenced private back garden (with raised gardening bed and storage shed) which is perfect for cookouts and entertaining, or just quiet relaxation to enjoy those warm summer and fall evenings. The large, attached garage has electric and an overhead door opener. For peace-of-mind, a 12-month APHW home warranty is offered by seller.  Transferable waterproofing warranty also included. All this and a convenient location just moments away from scenic Walnut Beach on Lake Erie, the Kent State campus, schools, medical facilities and the historical and trendy Bridge Street district with its restaurants, shops, picturesque harbor and much more. This wonderful and welcoming home is just waiting for you - come and see it today!
